\id PHM - Toma Bible 
\h Filemɔn 
\toc1 Pɔle Ná-Sɛʋɛi É Teʋeni Filemɔn Ma 
\toc2 Filemɔn 
\toc3 Flm 
\mt2 Pɔle Ná-Sɛʋɛi  //  É Teʋeni 
\mt1 Filemɔn Ma 
\imt1 Sɛʋɛi lɔɔzeizuʋɛ ma woo mɔungiti 
\ip Sɛʋɛ zuɓuɠagi nii teʋegai Filemɔn ma, keelai Pɔle ɠa é sɛʋɛni (\xt 1:1\xt*). Pɔle ɠɛni kasoi ɠa, siɛgi zu é ɠɛni sɛʋɛi nii ɠɛɛzu la, kona ʋuulɔzita maazu ɠila (61) kɛɠala leʋegai ma, Kilista zɔlɔɔga ʋoluma. Efɛze nuiti ta-zɛʋɛi, ta Filipe nuiti tɔnɔi, ta Kolɔse nuiti tɔnɔi, naa ʋɛɛ Filemɔn nɔnɔi ʋa, ti-laasei pɛɛʋɛ ga kasoɠa zɛʋɛiti, tɔɔzei é ti zɛʋɛni siɛgi zu é ɠɛni la kasoi ɠa. 
\ip É sɛʋɛi nii leʋegɛ zunui ta ma, daa ga Filemɔn. Filemɔn ɠɛni ga Egilisii zu nui ta. Naa ʋolu é ɠɛni ga duɔ kɛɛɠɛi ta. Pɔle sɛʋɛi ɠɛɛni ma, ga é maanɛɛnɛ ga é mina faa zei ná-duɔi Wonezime ma, tɔɔzei naa ʋelani, é zeɠe Filemɔn ʋɔ bɛ. Ʋelei Wɔlɔme lɔgi zu vaiti ti ɠɛni la, zobogi ɠɛni Filemɔn ʋɛ ga é Wonezime ʋaa. Pɔle lada woozuɠulagiti boni, nii a kɛ Filemɔn iɲɔ ga é yeezei Wonezime wu, ga ɠɛɛɠɛloin ta, ta-ɓɔfaamai zu ta Kilista, é suvali vɔlɔ naa ma ga Filemɔn vaa bu, Wonezime ɗa botii ɠɛ Pɔle ɓɔɠɔi mu bɛ (\xt 1:13-14\xt*). 
\iot Unsosuʋɛ 
\io1 1. Pɔle ná-tuʋɔ gooi laazeelini Filemɔn ma (\xt 1:1-3\xt*). 
\io1 2. Naa ʋoluma, Pɔle maanɛɛnɛi wo Wonezime laaseigi zu ga Filemɔn yeezei bu ga ɠɛɛɠɛloin ta, ta-ɓɔfaamai zu ta Kilista (\xt 1:4-21\xt*). 
\io1 3. Pɔle gaaɓelagɛ ga é kisu vai wo ma ga toɠa pɔ é li é laali ma, é ná-tuʋɔ gooiti daazeeli ma (\xt 1:22-25\xt*). 
\c 1  
\s1 Tuʋɔ gooiti 
\p  
\v 1 Nɛ̀i gè ga Pɔle, nà ga kasoɠa nu, botii maaʋele ma gè kɛa Yesu Kilista ʋɛ, gá ade-ɠɛɛloin Timɔte, gá è luʋɔsu, Filemɔn, gi-nɛɛɲɔɠɔi, adɛi de botii ɠɛɛzu ʋɔɔma,  
\v 2 wa Apia ade-ʋaazeelai, ta Aalisipe, ada nii de kɔɔi ɠɔɔzu ʋɔɔma, ta Egilisii é gaalɛbai wosu ɗa-ʋɛlɛi wu.  
\v 3 Ade-Ɠɛɛ GALA ta de-Maliɠii Yesu Kilista ti zaalai la wo ma, ti ziilɛigi ve wo ʋɛ. 
\s1 Filemɔn ná-nɛɛbɛi ta ná-kidaaleʋei 
\p  
\v 4 Nà nà-GALAGI mamasu ɠɔ, gè ɗa ɠizɛ è zu nà-GALA falii zu,  
\v 5 mazɔlɔɔ nà ɗa-ɠidaaleʋe vai mɛnisu é lo Maliɠii Yesu ʋa, ta ɗa-nɛɛbɛi é lo GALA ná-nuiti pɛ ba.  
\v 6 Nà GALA falizu ga kpɔfaamai é ade ɠiliai ʋa ɗa-ɠidaaleʋei maaʋele ma, naa ɠula kɛlɛma ga kɛɛwotii. Nii a kɛ faa ʋagɔi kpein gá ɠɛ è liini kɛɛ vai ma Kilista ná-faa ma, naa ɠula kɛlɛma.  
\v 7 Kɛ̀ɛloun, ɗa-nɛɛbɛi gòla ɠoozunɛa, é ìɲɔdɔ, mazɔlɔɔ è GALA ná-nuiti ziilaaʋɛ. 
\s1 Pɔle maanɛɛnɛi wo fai  //  Wonezime ná-faa zu 
\p  
\v 8 Naa ɠa é ba, anɛɛ ni Kilista maaʋele ma, zobogi pɛ ka zèa, nii maanɛai è kɛ, gè è leve ma,  
\v 9 fizɔgɛ gè è maanɛɛnɛ nɛɛbɛi maaʋele ma, ʋelei gè la, nà Pɔle, kɛwola wɔlɔi, é ɓudɛ naa maazu, niizu nɛ̀i gè kasoi ɠa, Yesu Kilista ná-faa zu.  
\v 10 Nà è maanɛɛnɛzu dòin Wonezime ná-faa zu, nii zɛ̀gai kasoi ɠa ʋɛ, gè ɠɛ ga kɛɛɠɛ zɛnvui zu.  
\v 11 Mɔungi zu, tosu la ɠɛni ba è ʋɛ, kɛlɛ niizu toɠa è maavaa ɠɛ\f + \fr 1:11 \fq maavaa ɠɛ\ft : Wonezime laaseigi ʋoluʋɛ ɠa ga maavaa ɠɛ nui.\f* niina, é nà ɓalaagi màavaa ɠɛ. 
\p  
\v 12 Nà teʋesu è ma ʋolu, tɔun, toɠa niina eɠɛ zìi ɓɔɔɓɔgi.  
\v 13 A la nɛɛ bɛ̀ ga gè makɛ ɠobaʋɛ, siɛgi zu gè kasoi ɠa la Woo Niinɛ Ʋagɔi ma vaa zu, é ɗa botii ɠɛ bɛ̀ è-ʋotogi zu.  
\v 14 Kɛlɛ gè la kɛɛni gè ʋa naa ɠɛ, ni è la vaani bu, naa ɠa a kɛ ɗa-vaaɓɔɠɔi mina ɠɛ ga maaɓaa vaa, kɛlɛ kɛni é ɠɛ ga è-yiimai. 
\p  
\v 15 Tanisu Wonezime ɓe ge leʋeni è ʋa, é ɠɛ ga yeeɠɛɠala go, nii a kɛ è sɔlɔɔ ya, é yɛ è ya eyɛsu ɠɔ.  
\v 16 Mazɔlɔɔ é la mɔ ga duɔ ɲaka nɔ, kɛlɛ toɠa niina ga nui fizɔgai duɔi ʋa, é ɠɛ è ʋɛ, eɠɛ ɠɛɛɠɛloin nii gola nɛai è ʋɛ. Nɛɛʋɛ bɛ̀ gola, kɛlɛ maanɛɛʋɛ é nɛɛ è ʋɛ mɔnɔ gola, é leʋe duɔi ʋa, é ɠɛ ga è-ɠɛɛloin Maliɠii maaʋele ma. 
\p  
\v 17 Naa ɠa é ba, ni deɠɛmu ɗa sèɠezu ga è-wɔɔlai, yeezei bu, eɠɛʋelei ɗa yeezei la bù.  
\v 18 Ni a ɠɛna faa ɠɛɛni ga ɗe, ɓaa ni ɗa-ɠuye ɠa ma, naa leve nɔ̀un unma.  
\v 19 Nà Pɔle, nà ɓɔɠɔi zèeʋogi ɠa gè nii zɛʋɛzu la: Nà sala è ma. Gè la naa wosu è ma ga tɛi nà-kuyei ɠa é è ma, ɗa ɓɔɠɔi ɗa ga nɔ̀nɔ.  
\v 20 Ungo, kɛ̀ɛloun, niima vaaɓɔɠɔi ɠɛ bɛ̀ da-ɠilibalai maaʋele ma da Maliɠii, è zìila da-ɠilibalai maaʋele ma da Kilista.  
\v 21 Nà niima zɛʋɛi ɠɛɛzu è ma ladalai zu, ga nii gè bosu è ma, ɗa ʋaazu kɛɛzu é ɓudɛ naa maazu.  
\v 22 Naa pɛ poluma, pɛlɛ ɠɛʋele ɓɛtɛ bɛ̀, ʋɛ nà ɠɛ ɲiizu ná, mazɔlɔɔ dàaʋɛ da ga, wa-ƓALA faliiti maaʋele ma, nà ma zobo sɔlɔɔsu, gè ʋaa wo ʋɔ bɛ. 
\s1 Tuʋɔ gaaɓelagiti 
\p  
\v 23 Epafelase, gi kasoi ɠa ʋɛ, Yesu Kilista ná-faa zu, toɠa è luʋɔsu,  
\v 24 ta Maleke ɓalaagi, ta Alisitaake, ta Demase, ta Luke, gɛiti gi botii ɠɛɛzu ʋɔɔma. 
\p  
\v 25 Maliɠii Yesu Kilista ná-zaalai yɛ wo ʋa.